        <section name="Mod4j 1.0.1 Upgrade Notes">

            <p>The following upgrade steps are needed if you want to upgrade your project from Mod4j 1.0.0 to Mod4j
                1.0.1.</p>
                
            <subsection name="Upgrade Mod4j Eclipse plug-in ">
                <ol>
                    <li>Open Eclipse and un-install all the previous installed Mod4j Eclipse features.</li>
                    <li>Now you can install the new version (1.0.1.200904141521) of the Mod4j Eclipse features via the Mod4j update site: 
                         <br/>
                         <b>http://mod4j.org/updatesite</b>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </subsection>
        </section>
